mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="微软雅黑" >UE5.6 官方第一人称射击游戏模板</font></span></b><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="微软雅黑" >，围绕</font> <font face="微软雅黑" >Gameplay Ability System（GAS）扩展一套支持多模型、多 Montage、预测与回滚的动画播放同步方案。</font></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><b><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="微软雅黑" >目标主要包括：</font></span></b><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;mso-spacerun:'yes';" >&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;margin-left:18.0000pt;
